        "description": {
          "value": "<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"2876\" > <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Innate Spellcasting.</span></span> <p>The deva's spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">17</span>). The deva can innately cast the following spells, requiring only verbal components:</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><ul class=\"rd__list rd__list-hang-notitle\"><li class=\"rd__li  rd__li-spell\"><p>At will: @spell[detect evil and good]</p></li><li class=\"rd__li  rd__li-spell\"><p>1/day each: @spell[commune], @spell[raise dead]</p></li></ul></div><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>",
